{"name": "odoo-addon-sale-automatic-workflow-job", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-sale-automatic-workflow-job", "version": "16.0.1.0.0.8", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo-addon-queue-job", "odoo-addon-sale-automatic-workflow", "odoo"], "summary": "Execute sale automatic workflows in queue jobs", "upload_time": 1705731381}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fsale--workflow-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/sale-workflow\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/16.0/sale_automatic_workflow_job\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/sale-workflow-16-0/sale-workflow-16-0-sale_automatic_workflow_job\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/sale-workflow&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Sale Automatic Workflow Job\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:835ec0b4caca6a48c2072677f19a54fd29a7af3311d108a9ff21a841ad686eec\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nUse Queue Jobs to process the Sales Automatic Workflow actions.\n\nThe default behavior of the automatic workflow module is to use a\nscheduled action that searches all the record that need a workflow\naction and sequentially process all of them.\n\nIt can hit some limits when the number of records is too high.\n\nThis module keeps the scheduled action to search the records, but\ninstead of directly executing the actions (confirm a sales order,\ncreate invoices for a sales order, validate invoices, ...), it\ncreates one job per operation to do.\n\nIt uses an identity key on the jobs so it will not create the same\njob for the same record and same operation twice.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues/new?body=module:%20sale_automatic_workflow_job%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Guewen Baconnier \\<<mailto:guewen.baconnier@camptocamp.com>>\n- Saran Lim. \\<<mailto:saranl@ecosoft.co.th>>\n- Kitti U. \\<<mailto:kittiu@ecosoft.co.th>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/sale-workflow](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/16.0/sale_automatic_workflow_job) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.models.automatic_workflow_job", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.models..automatic_workflow_job", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.models.queue_job", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.models..queue_job", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.models.queue_job", "documentation": ["Copyright 2020 Ecosoft Co., Ltd. (http://ecosoft.co.th)", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.models.queue_job.QueueJob", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.models.queue_job.QueueJob._related_action_sale_automatic_workflow", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.models.queue_job.QueueJob._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Job status and result"]}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow_job.tests.test_auto_workflow_job", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sal